node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by New Zealand Guide on August 14, 2021 tagging @kamanaqt. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
WIN an incredible getaway for 2 in Queenstown, thanks to @kamanaqt! Includes 2 nights accommodation, daily breakfast, a hot tub experience with a view and a three-course dinner, valued at $1,000. You will absolutely love this slice of paradise!⁣
⁣
To enter: ⁣
1) Follow @kamanaqt⁣
2) Tag a friend who would love this. Each comment is an entry.⁣
⁣
Prize includes: ⁣
🌄 2 nights stay with @kamanaqt for 2⁣
🥐 Daily breakfast for 2 with the most incredible Queenstown views⁣
♨️ 1 @kamanaqt Soak private pool session for 2⁣
🍴 1 three-course tasting dinner for 2 at the stunning @nest_qt⁣
⁣
Get ready for the most memorable Queenstown getaway, thanks to @kamanaqt! This is the ultimate getaway for 2, complete with all the luxury! Settle in with a 2 night stay at @kamanaqt. Start each day with a full breakfast in the most beautiful restaurant space with mountain and lake views. Take it all in with a Kamana Soak private session, in a hot tub perched on the hill. Indulge in a truly delicious three-course tasting dinner in Kamana's @nest_qt. We're so excited to be partnering with @kamanaqt to bring you this awesome prize package!⁣
⁣
Each comment is an entry! The winner will be drawn on Thursday 19th August. T&C’s are as follows: ⁣
- Prize is for 2 people⁣
- Room type is to be decided by Kamana Lakehouse and is based on availability⁣
- Prize can be redeemed between 19th August - 20th December 2021 and bookings are subject to availability⁣
- Black-out dates may apply⁣
- Dinner excludes alchohol⁣
- The winner will be contacted directly by @newzealandguide ⁣
- This giveaway is not in any way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Instagram ⁣
- This is a paid partnership⁣
⁣
Good luck! 🙌

--------------------

Winner is now drawn. Congratulations @annalise.stevens 🙌🎉
